<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 22:06:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>塞法迪首席拉比谴责以色列士兵不尊重清真寺的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</link><description>拉比伊扎克·约瑟夫（Yitzhak Yosef）写信给以色列国防军首席拉比，称士兵亵渎圣地的图像“对以色列人民及其在世界上的形象造成损害”，并表示应该向士兵解释“成员的感受”其他宗教的信仰不应受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 21:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列退伍军人在特别选举中被任命为共和党候选人，取代乔治·桑托斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</link><description>拿骚县议员、前以色列伞兵马兹·皮利普(Mazi Pilip)将在桑托斯空出的席位的特别选举中与民主党前国会议员汤姆·索兹(Tom Suozzi)对决</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 20:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅仅是否认暴行和悲凉：为什么这次巴勒斯坦民意调查很重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</link><description>在 10 月 7 日之前，巴勒斯坦政策和调查研究中心的这些发现将被认为对两国解决方案不利。现在他们应该给予安慰</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲各地因恐怖阴谋联合调查逮捕七人，嫌疑人与哈马斯有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</link><description>摩萨德周四在一份声明中表示，丹麦因“代表”哈马斯针对平民的恐怖阴谋而逮捕了七人。目前尚不清楚这七次逮捕是否指的是在欧洲进行的所有逮捕，或者是否还有丹麦当局未报告的其他逮捕事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</guid></item><item><title>随着中国站在巴勒斯坦一边，加沙战争可能会加强以色列与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</link><description>中国媒体告诉世界，美国因欧洲和加沙战争而分心，可能会在一月份选举前危及台湾。然而，中国回应的一个副作用可能是促使以色列和台湾走得更近</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩南部的以色列缓冲区？贝鲁特政客忙于政党政治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-buffer-zone-in-south-lebanon-beirut-politicians-are-busy-with-party-politics/0000018c-686d-de5e-a3ef-6beddf560000</link><description>即使找到了将真主党赶出边境的纲领，黎巴嫩政界人士可能更关注谁填补该国空缺的总统职位，因为他们的政治和经济状况使得他们不太可能采取行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-buffer-zone-in-south-lebanon-beirut-politicians-are-busy-with-party-politics/0000018c-686d-de5e-a3ef-6beddf560000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的加沙堡垒是世界上独一无二的战场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-gaza-fortress-is-a-battlefield-like-no-other-in-the-world/0000018c-695a-db38-a9fc-e9fabcff0000</link><description>任何人如果问为什么拥有如此先进能力的以色列军队需要在加沙发动地面行动才能击败哈马斯，那么他并不了解该领土的独特挑战。以色列的所有选择都是致命的</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-gaza-fortress-is-a-battlefield-like-no-other-in-the-world/0000018c-695a-db38-a9fc-e9fabcff0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争紧张局势扰乱校园；布朗抗议者被捕；哈弗福德大楼被占用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</link><description>数十名学生因抗议以色列在加沙的行动而拒绝离开大学大楼而被捕，这是一个月内的第二轮逮捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</guid></item><item><title>禁止暴力定居者：美国和欧洲制定拒绝入境者的标准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</link><description>随着针对暴力以色列定居者的国际行动势头增强，美国、英国和欧盟正在寻找方法，对那些在西岸对巴勒斯坦人实施暴力的人实施和执行签证禁令和其他限制</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 16:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称10月7日的死亡人数与奥斯陆的死亡人数相同——更多的操纵和逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</link><description>总理没有详细说明他的说法背后的计算，但进一步的检查表明这些数据可以被操纵，并且需要背景。最重要的是，内塔尼亚胡在这里也至少承担部分责任</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 14:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</guid></item><item><title>备受争议的汉娜·阿伦特奖颁奖典礼被推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</link><description>玛莎·格森因在美国杂志《纽约客》的一篇文章中发表言论而受到批评，据说他们在文中将加沙的局势与二战期间被占领的欧洲犹太人聚居区进行了比较</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</guid></item><item><title>拜登以色列和乌克兰政策背后的价值观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登对乌克兰和加沙战争及危机的处理堪称典范，迄今为止也是成功的。两国都很幸运，这些战争发生在一位既是自由干涉主义者又是现实主义者的领导人的领导下</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军与杰宁武装分子交火，三名巴勒斯坦人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</link><description>以色列士兵被拍摄到在难民营中使用清真寺扬声器向难民营居民发出呼吁，并唱光明节歌曲。以色列国防军表示，这些士兵立即被解除执行任务</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准2023年补充战时预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</link><description>该修正案以 58 票赞成、44 票反对的结果获得批准。内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团情报部长吉拉·加姆利尔缺席投票，利库德集团议员尤利·埃德尔斯坦最初投了赞成票，但后来要求修改投票以弃权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 12:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级官员建议遵循巴解组织官方立场承认以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/top-hamas-official-suggests-recognizing-israel-following-official-plo-stance/0000018c-67e4-d798-adac-e7ef81fd0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚阿布·马祖克在接受​​《中东观察报》采访时所表达的立场是否代表了该组织的立场。他还为哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击辩护，并表示这实现了该组织的目标：“每个人都在谈论巴勒斯坦事业”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 11:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/top-hamas-official-suggests-recognizing-israel-following-official-plo-stance/0000018c-67e4-d798-adac-e7ef81fd0000</guid></item><item><title>哈大沙妇女组织谴责红十字会未能救治被哈马斯扣押在加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hadassah-women-group-slams-red-cross-failure-to-treat-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-67b3-de43-affd-f7b3080a0000</link><description>美国妇女犹太复国主义组织哈大沙致信正在访问以色列的红十字会主席：“红十字会以前是否曾以如此公然的方式未能照顾人质和武装侵略的受害者，或者这种待遇是保留的吗？”对于从以色列被绑架的人？</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hadassah-women-group-slams-red-cross-failure-to-treat-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-67b3-de43-affd-f7b3080a0000</guid></item><item><title>对加沙泥潭的恐惧：以色列是否陷入另一场长期消耗战？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/fears-of-a-gaza-quagmire-is-israel-in-another-long-war-of-attrition/0000018c-6322-d798-adac-e7af94c90000</link><description>政治和军事层面幻想一场长期战争，没有任何结束计划，忽视人质，并相信公众已经习惯了军事损失</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/fears-of-a-gaza-quagmire-is-israel-in-another-long-war-of-attrition/0000018c-6322-d798-adac-e7af94c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周三在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-674f-de43-affd-f74ffe910000</link><description>周三，来自哈里什的 38 岁军士长伊莱沙·莱文施滕 (Elisha Levinshtern) 在加沙地带南部被一枚反坦克导弹击中身亡。莱文施滕身后留下了他的妻子哈达斯和他的六个孩子</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:23:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-674f-de43-affd-f74ffe910000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：“我希望以色列专注于如何拯救加沙平民的生命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-live/hostages-families-demand-clarification-from-netanyahu-over-decision-not-to-hold-talks/0000018c-65b5-de43-affd-f5b7d6250000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问抵达以色列，在周五与阿巴斯会面之前会见战时内阁 ■ 拜登希望以色列重点关注如何拯救加沙平民 ■ 摩萨德称，有七人因策划针对犹太人的恐怖袭击而在欧洲被捕哈马斯 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称加沙有 18,608 人死亡、50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-live/hostages-families-demand-clarification-from-netanyahu-over-decision-not-to-hold-talks/0000018c-65b5-de43-affd-f5b7d6250000</guid></item><item><title>舒贾耶战役暴露了以色列军队的缺陷，但并不表明加沙战斗发生了变化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-knows-us-better-than-we-do/0000018c-64cf-d798-adac-e4ef2dc40000</link><description>以色列军队从未在人口稠密的城市地区经历过如此长时间的战斗，因此尚无法宣布控制加沙地带北部。然而，战斗性质的真正改变不是由哈马斯带来的，而是由美国加大压力带来的</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-knows-us-better-than-we-do/0000018c-64cf-d798-adac-e4ef2dc40000</guid></item></channel></rss>